    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIR\nCALIFORNIA\nSystem Timetable\nEffective July 15, 1980\nNow serving Los Angeles\nInternational Airport",
      "Now serving Los Angeles\nInternational Airport\nNow serving Los Angeles International\nAirport.\nWe're growing to bring convenient,\neconomical air travel to more places in\nthe West.\nSo Air California is making it easy\nto fly by linking Los Angeles with\nFresno, Monterey, and San Francisco.\nWe're Air California. And we want\neveryone to fly."
